headline: TrueBlue Recognized as a Leader in Industrial Staffing by Everest Group
summary: TACOMA, Wash., July 31, 2025--TrueBlue (NYSE: TBI), a leading provider of specialized workforce solutions, today announced that its flagship staffing brand, PeopleReady, has been named a Leader in Everest Group’s US Contingent Talent and Strategic Solutions PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025 – Industrial.
